name: HELIUM Mk.II
details:
ANALOG OCTAVE DISTORTION PEDALThe HELIUM MKII is an Octavia style distortion pedal coupled with an intense octave up effect, this updated version of the legendary HELIUM features a second WOLF setting to augment the original pedal’s two position octave sonic palette. The Mark II features a smaller footprint to fit into your pedalboard.
